These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 5

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-1::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, lemonade, sprite, water
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: tennis, baseball, weightlifting, skiing
1. the person drinking lemonade is somewhere to the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##5
2. the person who's sport is skiing is on the left or right of the person who's sport is tennis##3
3. the person who's sport is tennis is in an odd position##4
4. the person drinking water is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is skiing##5
5. the person who's sport is tennis is the person drinking lemonade##1
6. the person drinking sprite is the person who's sport is baseball##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |       2       |     3     |   4    |
| Beverage      | water  | hot-chocolate | lemonade  | sprite |
| Sport   | weightlifting | skiing      | tennis | baseball |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-2::.
4 different games are played: bridge, poker, billiard, monopoly
4 different pets are kept: bird, chinchilla, goat, horse
1. the person playing poker is between the owner of the bird and the owner of the horse##2
2. the person playing monopoly is somewhere to the left of the owner of the horse##5
3. the owner of the bird is on the right of the owner of the goat##1
4. the owner of the bird is on the right of the person playing monopoly##1
5. the owner of the chinchilla is on the left of the person playing bridge##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |     3      |     4      |
| Game   | monopoly | billiard | poker   | bridge |
| Pet           | goat      | bird    | chinchilla | horse      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-3::.
There 4 different types of food: cabbage, corn, peach, potato
4 different games are played: backgammon, snooker, chess, billiard
1. the person eating corn is the person playing snooker##1
2. the person playing billiard is on the right of the person eating corn##1
3. the person playing chess is somewhere to the left of the person playing backgammon##5
4. the person playing backgammon is on the left or right of the person eating peach##3
5. the person eating potato is somewhere to the right of the person playing billiard##5
6. the person eating corn is somewhere to the left of the person playing chess##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |  1   |    2    |     3     |   4    |
| Food        | corn | cabbage | peach     | potato |
| Game   | snooker  | billiard   | chess | backgammon    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-4::.
4 different pets are kept: guinea-pig, frog, ferret, fish
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: crime, epic, family, romance
1. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left of the owner of the frog##1
2. the owner of the fish is somewhere to the right of the person watching family movies##5
3. the owner of the guinea-pig is between the person watching romance movies and the person watching epic movies##2
4. the person watching family movies is on the left or right of the person watching romance movies##3
5. the person watching romance movies is the owner of the ferret##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |    3    |      4      |
| Pet         | ferret | guinea-pig | frog | fish |
| Movie-Genre   | romance   | family     | epic    | crime       |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-5::.
House: cape-cod, victorian, tower, townhouse
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: disaster, mystery, western, zombie
1. the townhouse house is somewhere to the left of the person watching disaster movies##5
2. the townhouse house is on the left or right of the tower house##3
3. the tower house is somewhere to the left of the cape-cod house##5
4. the person watching western movies is on the right of the person watching disaster movies##1
5. the person watching disaster movies is on the left or right of the victorian house##3
6. the townhouse house is on the right of the person watching mystery movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2    |    3     |    4    |
| House          | tower | townhouse   | cape-cod   | victorian    |
| Movie-Genre   | mystery  | zombie | disaster | western |

