.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-6::.
There 4 different types of food: blueberry, eggplant, cauliflower, asparagus
There are 4 different nationalities: japanese, russian, thai, turkish
1. the person eating asparagus is in an odd position##4
2. the person eating blueberry is somewhere to the left of the turkish##5
3. the turkish is between the person eating asparagus and the thai##2
4. the person eating cauliflower is on the right of the japanese##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2      |       3        |     4     |
| Food           | blueberry | eggplant | asparagus | cauliflower |
| Nationality   | thai        | turkish     | japanese       | russian   |

