.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-7::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: ambient, hip-hop, jazz, salsa
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: march, october, june, april
1. the person who's birthday is in october is the fan of salsa##1
2. the fan of ambient is between the fan of hip-hop and the person who's birthday is in june##2
3. the person who's birthday is in march is in an even position##4
4. the person who's birthday is in april is somewhere to the left of the fan of ambient##5
5. the fan of ambient is in an even position##4
6. the fan of jazz is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in october##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |   3   |    4    |
| Music-Genre   | hip-hop | ambient  | jazz  | salsa   |
| Birthday           | april  | march | june | october |

