.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-8::.
There 4 different types of food: carrot, mango, pear, strawberry
There are 4 different favourite colors: ebony, amber, grey, blue
1. the person who likes amber is on the right of the person who likes blue##1
2. the person eating strawberry is somewhere to the left of the person who likes grey##5
3. the person eating strawberry is on the left or right of the person eating pear##3
4. the person eating mango is on the left of the person eating strawberry##1
5. the person who likes grey is somewhere to the left of the person who likes ebony##5

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |     2      |    3     |    4     |
| Food   | mango     | strawberry | pear     | carrot   |
| Color    | blue | amber  | grey | ebony |

