.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-9::.
4 different games are played: chess, billiard, whist, scrabble
There 4 different types of food: lemon, pear, potato, tomato
1. the person eating potato is on the right of the person playing chess##1
2. the person playing whist is on the left of the person playing scrabble##1
3. the person playing chess is on the left of the person playing whist##1
4. the person playing billiard is somewhere to the right of the person eating tomato##5
5. the person eating pear is somewhere to the right of the person eating lemon##5
6. the person eating lemon is somewhere to the left of the person eating potato##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |    2     |   3    |  4   |
| Game   | chess | whist | scrabble   | billiard |
| Food       | lemon       | potato   | tomato | pear |

