.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-10::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: dunhill, ritmeester, chaman, baccarat
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: soccer, surfing, water-polo, weightlifting
1. the chaman-smoker is on the left or right of the person who's sport is surfing##3
2. the person who's sport is soccer is somewhere to the left of the baccarat-smoker##5
3. the person who's sport is weightlifting is somewhere to the right of the ritmeester-smoker##5
4. the person who's sport is soccer is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is weightlifting##5
5. the person who's sport is surfing is somewhere to the left of the dunhill-smoker##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |       2       |   3    |     4      |
| Cigar   | ritmeester | chaman       | dunhill   | baccarat        |
| Sport      | surfing  | weightlifting | soccer | water-polo |

