.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-12::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: animation, epic, horror, spy
City: hannover, miami, colone, berlin
1. the person traveling to berlin is on the left of the person traveling to hannover##1
2. the person traveling to berlin is in an even position##4
3. the person watching spy movies is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to miami##5
4. the person watching animation movies is the person traveling to colone##1
5. the person watching spy movies is somewhere to the right of the person watching horror movies##5
6. the person traveling to miami is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2       |     3      |  4   |
| Movie-Genre   | animation | horror        | spy        | epic |
| City         | colone  | berlin | hannover | miami |

