2. the fan of gospel is somewhere to the right of the fan of ambient##5
3. the fan of gospel is in an odd position##4
4. the owner of the hamster is somewhere to the left of the fan of trance##5
5. the fan of trance is on the right of the owner of the hamster##1
6. the owner of the goldfish is the fan of trance##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |    3    |    4    |
| Pet         | hamster | goldfish | pony | turtle |
| Music-Genre   | ambient     | trance  | gospel  | soul    |

