.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-14::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: disaster, documentary, thriller, western
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: baseball, basketball, rugby, biathlon
1. the person watching disaster movies is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is rugby##5
2. the person watching thriller movies is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is baseball##5
3. the person who's sport is basketball is on the left of the person who's sport is biathlon##1
4. the person who's sport is biathlon is the person watching thriller movies##1
5. the person watching documentary movies is somewhere to the right of the person watching disaster movies##5
6. the person who's sport is basketball is on the left or right of the person who's sport is baseball##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |      3      |    4     |
| Movie-Genre   | western  | disaster | documentary | thriller |
| Sport   | rugby | baseball | basketball   | biathlon  |

