.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-15::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: filmmaking, gardening, puzzles, singing
The people use 4 different means of transport: ship, bike, motorbike, roller
1. the person who's hobby is singing is between the person who's hobby is puzzles and the person who's hobby is gardening##2
2. the person driving the ship is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is singing##3
3. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the right of the person who's hobby is singing##1
4. the person who's hobby is puzzles is somewhere to the right of the person driving the motorbike##5
5. the person driving the motorbike is somewhere to the left of the person driving the roller##5
6. the person driving the motorbike is on the left of the person driving the roller##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |    2     |      3       |     4     |
| Hobby   | filmmaking | puzzles  | singing      | gardening |
| Transport     | motorbike    | roller | bike | ship   |

