.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-17::.
There are 4 different nationalities: german, italian, thai, turkish
There are 4 different favourite colors: white, yellow, grey, ebony
1. the turkish is somewhere to the left of the person who likes ebony##5
2. the thai is the person who likes ebony##1
3. the person who likes white is on the right of the person who likes yellow##1
4. the turkish is somewhere to the right of the german##5
5. the person who likes grey is on the right of the italian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |    3    |  4   |
| Nationality   | german     | italian | turkish | thai |
| Color     | yellow | white    | grey    | ebony |

