.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-18::.
4 different pets are kept: snake, dog, hedgehog, mouse
There are 4 different nationalities: egyptian, french, nigerian, turkish
1. the nigerian is on the far left or far right##3
2. the egyptian is somewhere to the right of the turkish##5
3. the nigerian is somewhere to the left of the owner of the snake##5
4. the egyptian is somewhere to the left of the owner of the dog##5
5. the egyptian is on the left of the french##1
6. the owner of the snake is between the owner of the mouse and the french##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |    3     |       4       |
| Pet      | hedgehog     | mouse | snake     | dog |
| Nationality   | nigerian | turkish  | egyptian | french        |

