2. the person who's birthday is in december is somewhere to the right of the owner of the mouse##5
3. the owner of the hamster is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in march##5
4. the person who's birthday is in july is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in december##3
5. the owner of the mouse is on the right of the owner of the hamster##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |    2    |     3      |     4      |
