.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-20::.
4 different games are played: monopoly, scrabble, whist, mah-jongg
The people use 4 different means of transport: car, ship, skateboard, snowmobile
1. the person playing scrabble is somewhere to the left of the person driving the ship##5
2. the person playing monopoly is on the right of the person driving the snowmobile##1
3. the person driving the skateboard is in an odd position##4
4. the person driving the car is somewhere to the right of the person driving the ship##5
5. the person playing scrabble is somewhere to the left of the person driving the snowmobile##5
6. the person playing monopoly is between the person playing mah-jongg and the person driving the car##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |     2      |     3     |     4      |
| Game        | scrabble     | mah-jongg | monopoly | whist |
| Transport   | skateboard | snowmobile | ship      | car        |

 